{
  "texts": [
    "In this section, we first introduce recent developments in facialvideo-based methods for learning engagement prediction.",
    "We then discuss recent works of log-based methods on response data mining, including IRT and Knowledge Tracing, and how previous works handled student states.",
    "Finally, we propose a unified model using facial-video-based and log-based methods to improve student response prediction performance.",
    "There are primarily two trends in recent studies to improve the accuracy of the learning engagement prediction task.",
    "One is to use a more accurate pre-trained facial expression recognition model to extract robust facial features against face occlusion and variation."
  ]
}